{"tid":1347142,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"真心一句 元朗係支線","createTime":"2019-07-22T05:28:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T08:24:38.000Z","uid":90520,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c30cecc43d0e8dad59caaee54a8be9ed61f9f1c7","tid":1347142,"uid":90520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:28:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">元朗係支線？</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">屌你老母啦</span>]</span><br />\n就算係支線又點？<br />\n依架畀人恰到上心口啊<br />\n狗隻嗰邊你都可以話唔去就避到<br />\n玩hit&amp;run 撚狗咁撚<br />\n你老母 依架返屋企都冇啦啦畀你<span style=\"font-size: large;\">打柒？</span><br />\n香港人自己友打香港人？<br />\n趁勇武去咗西環 係後門打鳩啲和理非婦孺？<br />\n<br />\n認真 醒少少都知元朗事件係拎黎<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">轉移視線</span></span><br />\n所以呢？又點啊？食屎啦<br />\n主線係長期作戰 開咗個頭 慢慢再打<br />\n但呢單突發事件 一定要快啲搞掂<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">對外前 先對內</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">攘外必先安内</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">727 元朗見</span></span>"},{"pid":"ff5afd1d9c4a898efe795e89f8e40d20ab894e0b","tid":1347142,"uid":90520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:30:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fa582969f1093bf27ac1d9ea281b952e105f9468","tid":1347142,"uid":90520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:31:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4c90d7f5c5f5d736ef7a85b4dcb44f47d955c7c5","tid":1347142,"uid":15129,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:31:09.000Z","msg":"上環暴力鎮壓 <br />\n元朗恐怖襲擊<br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"2a4b387682f32cdae8ae9d2047f51cba389bca2b","tid":1347142,"uid":90520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c90d7f5c5f5d736ef7a85b4dcb44f47d955c7c5","tid":1347142,"uid":15129,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"ci